<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>BBMS | About us</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>

  <div class="container">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
      <img src="images/hospital.avif" style="width: 35vw; height: 35vw;">
    </div>
    <p class="display-7 text-center" style="font-weight: 300;">
      At our Blood Bank System, we are driven by a deep commitment to saving lives and improving the well-being of individuals and communities. With years of experience in the field, our dedicated team understands the critical importance of a reliable blood supply. We leverage cutting-edge technology and robust infrastructure to ensure seamless coordination between donors, recipients, and healthcare providers. Our mission is to provide a user-friendly platform that empowers individuals to become blood donors and connect them with those in urgent need. Join us in our lifesaving journey and make a tangible difference in the lives of countless individuals who depend on the generosity of people like you.
    </p>

    <h4 class="display-6 text-center">Below are some of our services</h4>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card custom-card">
          <img src="images/give.jpeg" style="width: 10vw; height: 10vw;">
          <p class="display-7">Donate Blood</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card custom-card">
          <img src="images/hosp.jpeg" style="width: 10vw; height: 10vw;">
          <p class="display-7">Request For Blood</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card custom-card">
          <img src="images/records.jpeg" style="width: 10vw; height: 10vw;">
          <p class="display-7">Manage Blood Records</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div> 

  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>